citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:26:26.000Z","msg":"中金國瑞岩岩係灣仔開左新office"},{"pid":"e5d66beed653fe497a8536bcf46d9363646f710f","tid":1256322,"uid":104804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:26:55.000Z","msg":"升咁耐終於跌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292f7aeb864a7374e72f38062a94b2596068cbab","tid":1256322,"uid":265881,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:29:22.000Z","msg":"支那不嬲係一個好大既賭場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都係度互相呃呃騙騙"},{"pid":"9e96b34f159c7184999bf6e1f3f7243a979bd192","tid":1256322,"uid":61520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:30:36.000Z","msg":"[緊急廣傳]DQ確認書殺入區議會選舉諮詢   今晚就係！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1256230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1256230</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6595ba04ea5936f87b8db3858b0cc7074b944c75","tid":1256322,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25be66fd184fe379d10363fa4d45f5151f07a239","tid":1256322,"uid":128417,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:32:32.000Z","msg":"仲有呢單<br />\n又有招行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》報道，美國法官裁定3間中國銀行試圖拒絕遵守就違反北韓制裁令的傳召，可能觸發禁止中國其中一間大型銀行接觸美國金融系統。<br />\n<br />\n報道指未能確認該3間銀行名稱，但法院裁決的詳情與2017年民事財產沒收行動相同。美國司法部當年指控交銀(<a href=\"http://03328.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F03328.HK&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443qEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=f4bd29cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">03328.HK</a>)    、招行   及上海浦發銀行(600000.SH)與1間香港公司有聯繫，該公司被指為遭制裁的北韓國營朝鮮貿銀行清洗逾1億美元。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，面臨被制裁風險的銀行為上海浦發銀行，該行的擁有權結構、美國業務有限及涉及與其他銀行的行為，與裁決中擬制裁的銀行相同。上海浦發銀行在美國沒有分支，僅保留帳戶處理美元交易。<br />\n<br />\n有關調查中國銀行是否協助北韓核系統，正值中美貿易關係惡化，貿易談判破裂引發美國關稅及其他措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.948449/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.948449%2F2&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443qEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=63a488d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.948449/2</a>"},{"pid":"ed5ec17e0b477a3e0ee5c7d72e0ce56644601299","tid":1256322,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:32:32.000Z","msg":"托管行呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點會唔見晒D貨?"},{"pid":"2d40aa3131728301b37cffed133b8d0957efc5c1","tid":1256322,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0143726cfde4ca599e8c6c00974c99ef0207f1ea","tid":1256322,"uid":35233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:26:26.000Z","msg":"中金國瑞岩岩係灣仔開左新office"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:33:06.000Z","msg":"咩玩法"},{"pid":"d0497faabd0158a9a9842e3b489bce6e6b3100c5","tid":1256322,"uid":18955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"高價買垃圾<br />\n而垃圾就用自己控制嘅戶口出貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb773839578131bea89a8c33bf946d6533ee6f8b","tid":1256322,"uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:38:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>農行39億票據變報紙</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/1/26/n4626051.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F16%2F1%2F26%2Fn4626051.htm&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443qEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=4ca57e33\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/1/26/n4626051.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e12fe52d55b3664b32b87597b0f32b13eaba352a","tid":1256322,"uid":59586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ed5ec17e0b477a3e0ee5c7d72e0ce56644601299","tid":1256322,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"